description: Cancels the specified Reserved Instance listing in the Reserved Instance Marketplace. For more information, see Sell in the Reserved Instance Marketplace in the Amazon EC2 User Guide.

parameters.name: ReservedInstancesListingId
parameters.description: The ID of the Reserved Instance listing.

nested_items.name: ClientToken
nested_items.description: A unique, case-sensitive key supplied by the client to ensure that the request is idempotent. For more information, see Ensuring Idempotency.

nested_items.name: CreateDate
nested_items.description: The time the listing was created.

nested_items.name: InstanceCounts
nested_items.description: The number of instances in this state.

nested_items.name: InstanceCount
nested_items.description: The number of listed Reserved Instances in the state specified by the state.

nested_items.name: State
nested_items.description: The states of the listed Reserved Instances.

nested_items.name: PriceSchedules
nested_items.description: The price of the Reserved Instance listing.

nested_items.name: Active
nested_items.description: The current price schedule, as determined by the term remaining for the Reserved Instance in the listing.

nested_items.name: CurrencyCode
nested_items.description: The currency for transacting the Reserved Instance resale. At this time, the only supported currency is USD.

nested_items.name: Price
nested_items.description: The fixed price for the term.

nested_items.name: Term
nested_items.description: The number of months remaining in the reservation. For example, 2 is the second to the last month before the capacity reservation expires.

nested_items.name: ReservedInstancesId
nested_items.description: The ID of the Reserved Instance.

nested_items.name: ReservedInstancesListingId
nested_items.description: The ID of the Reserved Instance listing.

nested_items.name: Status
nested_items.description: The status of the Reserved Instance listing.

nested_items.name: StatusMessage
nested_items.description: The reason for the current status of the Reserved Instance listing. The response can be blank.

nested_items.name: Tags
nested_items.description: Any tags assigned to the resource.

nested_items.name: UpdateDate
nested_items.description: The last modified timestamp of the listing.
